Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Ford presidency
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8jrn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jun 1975
Ford is making a better job of his presidency than most voters expected. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less